韩国新冠肺炎患者升破2000人，隔离治疗负压病床告急。
South Korea's new crown pneumonia patients rose to 2,000 people, isolation treatment of negative pressure hospital beds.
界面新闻                      。
Interface news.
界面新闻。
Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
图片来源：Yonhap“ 《东亚日报》指出，截至27日上午，加上民间医疗机构，韩国总共仅有1077张负压病床，已远少于确诊病例人数。
"Source: Yonhap" As of the morning of July 27, with the addition of civilian medical institutions, there were only 1,077 negative-pressure beds, far fewer than the number of confirmed cases, "Yonhap said.
”韩国中央防疫对策本部2月28日通报，截至当天上午9时，韩国较昨日新增256例新冠病毒感染病例，累计确诊2022例，死亡13例，治愈26例。
As of 9: 00 a.m. on the same day, the Republic of Korea had 256 new cases of Crested Virus infection, a cumulative total of 2,022 confirmed cases, 13 deaths and 26 cases cured.
在新增的256例病例中，分别有182例和49例来自大邱和庆北地区。
Of the 256 new cases, 182 were from Daegu and 49 from Gyeongbei.
截至目前，除确诊患者外，韩国接受病毒检测的人数累计68918人，其中44167人的检测结果呈阴性，其余24751人的结果还未出炉。
So far, 68,918 people have been tested for the virus in South Korea, of whom 44167 have tested negative. The results for the remaining 24,751 are still pending.
来源：韩国中央防疫对策本部目前，韩国超八成确诊病例集中在大邱和庆北这两个相邻地区，分别有两个主要的传染发生地：新天地大邱教会和庆北清道郡大南医院。
Source: Korea Central Preventive Measures Headquarters At present, more than 80% of the confirmed cases in Korea are concentrated in the neighboring areas of Daegu and Gyeongbei, where two major infections occur: Taegu Church in Xintiandi and Daonan Hospital in Qingdao County, Gyeongbei Province.
在截至28日上午9点累计确诊的2022例新冠肺炎病例中，分别有1314例和394例来自大邱和庆北地区，占比65%和19.5%。
Of the 2,022 cumulative cases of new crown pneumonia confirmed as of 9: 00 am on the 28th, 1314 and 394 respectively came from Daegu and Gyeongbei regions, accounting for 65% and 19.5% respectively.
在截至27日上午9点累计确诊的1595例新冠肺炎病例中，分别有731例与114例与新天地大邱教会及清道郡大南医院有关，占比45.8%和7.1%。
Of the total of 1,595 cases of new crown pneumonia confirmed by 9: 00 am on the 27th, 731 cases were related to Taegu Church in Xintiandi and Dainan Hospital in Qingdao County, accounting for 45.8% and 7.1% respectively.
韩国卫生部门自26日起已对全国约21万名新天地教会信徒展开检测。
South Korean health authorities have been testing about 210,000 believers in Xintiandi Church nationwide since 26.
韩国中央防疫对策本部长郑银敬27日说，目前9000余名新天地大邱教会信徒中，1299例有症状待查病例已完成标本采集，预计这两天新病例的数量还会激增。
Zheng Yingjing, minister of the Central Anti-epidemic Policy of the Republic of Korea, said Monday that 1,299 of the 9,000 Taegu believers in Xintiandi had already collected specimens, and the number of new cases is expected to soar in the next two days.
与大南医院有关的病例数量近几日则未见明显增加，该医院共有103名患者、10名医护人员与1名患者家属确诊，但在截至目前的13例死亡病例中，有7例均出现在该医院，另有4例与新天地教会有关。
There has been no significant increase in the number of cases associated with the hospital in recent days, with 103 patients, 10 health-care workers and one patient's family members diagnosed, but 7 of the 13 deaths so far have occurred at the hospital and 4 cases are related to Xintiandi Church.
据韩联社27日报道，随着国内感染新冠病毒的确诊病例不断增多，韩国民营医疗机构已纷纷开放负压病房等设施，以缓解国家定点医疗机构的负压病房紧缺问题。
As the number of confirmed cases of infection with the new crown virus has increased, private medical institutions in South Korea have opened negative pressure wards and other facilities to ease the shortage of negative pressure wards in state-designated medical institutions.
据韩国医疗界当天消息，该国规模最大的民营医疗机构——首尔峨山医院和三星首尔医院当天分别开放6间和22间负压病房，供新冠肺炎确诊患者接受治疗。
Seoul Asan Hospital and Samsung Seoul Hospital, the country's largest private medical institutions, opened 6 and 22 negative pressure wards on the same day, respectively, for treatment of patients diagnosed with pneumonia, medical sources said.
延世大学医疗院则决定从3月2日起为新冠肺炎病例提供22间负压病房，首尔圣母医院也在讨论相关事宜。
The Yenshi University Medical Institute has decided to provide 22 negative pressure wards for new crown pneumonia cases from March 2. Notre Dame Hospital in Seoul is also discussing the matter.
《东亚日报》当天早些时候曾指出，加上民间医疗机构，韩国现有的感染者隔离治疗用负压病床总共仅1077张，已远少于累计确诊的病例人数，必须尽快重新制定医疗资源分配战略，为可能出现的“持久战”做好准备。
Earlier in the day, the newspaper noted that with the addition of civilian medical institutions, the number of existing negative-pressure beds for isolation and treatment of infected persons in South Korea was only 1,077, far less than the cumulative number of confirmed cases.
据韩联社报道，27日出现的第13例死亡病例便是因病床不足，在等待住院的过程中病重不治。
The 13th fatality on the 27th was due to a lack of beds and severe illness while waiting to be hospitalized, KFL reported.
